  <ThingDef ParentName="OEBaseRosner">
    <defName>OE_Rosner</defName>
    <label>rosner</label>
    <description>An Obsidia giant mammal with giant horn, domesticated in ancient times for fur, meat and milk. Rosner are peaceful creatures that can be tamed. But at the same time, they are very easy to enrage if you attack them. Once angered, its massive strength and sharp horn make it a brutal opponent.</description>
    <race>
      <meatLabel>rosner meat</meatLabel>
    </race>
  </ThingDef>

